title: Bug 110566 - Wrong data set result returned when an invalid filter expression is set for row[0]
description: When setting a filter expression like 'row[0] equals to 0' or when passing an invalid filter expression, the system returns an incorrect data set result or a null result set.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Set a filter expression like 'row[0] equals to 0'.
2. Observe the returned data set result or a null result set.
